    Title: I Ching
  Title: The Man of Many Qualities
Title: Creativity
---
At the outset, the man is unknown, like a dragon lying hidden. The occasion
is not yet ripe for his appearance. He is not moved by public opinion and
the desire for fame. He hides his time in self-confidence and silence.
